hen people get in financial trouble, the cure for finding debt relief can often be worse than the problem. As a non-profit organization, this company&#39;s first goal is to educate consumers about debt issues and provide credit counseling services. For those times when a debt problem is nearly beyond repair, Debt Consolidation Connection is accredited and licensed to handle these debt management services. Being a non-profit stops them from helping out in situations that require debt settlement.","This debt relief service negotiates with creditors on your behalf to decrease the interest rates on your debts as much as possible, and it attempts to remove late fees and penalties. It&#39;s possible to eliminate any previous late fees. The cost of Debt Consolidation Connection&#39;s services is based on the amount of debt you have and which state you live in. We look for a money-back guarantee from companies that offer debt consolidation help, but because this debt management company does not offer settlement plans, it doesn&#39;t offer a money-back guarantee either.","The main website for Debt Consolidation Connection is easy to follow. It has several tools for budget planning and a calculator so you can compile your debt and find an average interest rate to see how long it would take to repay them. This service fits the standard of other debt management agencies in that creditors pay a commission in return for Debt Consolidation Connection&#39;s assistance in getting you to repay a significant portion of your debts.","Debt Consolidation Connection&#39;s certified credit counselors are able to set up a debt management plan for clients when the situation calls for it. They are also able to assist consumers with less drastic credit counseling matters when a debt management plan isn&#39;t necessary. Its freedom to offer other options is one of the best arguments for turning to a firm like this, at least initially, before turning to commercial debt management companies, which have a more pressing interest in getting customers into debt management or debt settlement arrangements.","Debt Consolidation Connection gives specific advice that will allow many consumers to get their debts under control, including budgeting and the systematic elimination of credit card and other unsecured debts. The company even offers advice for restructuring home mortgage loans that have unfavorable terms.","Customer service is available by both telephone and email. We found the representatives to be generally helpful but less forthcoming and empathetic than those we dealt with at some other companies. Debt Consolidation Connection&#39;s website can be an invaluable asset in answering debt and financial questions that most people have and in promoting healthy money-management habits. All information collected on Debt Consolidation Connection&#39;s website is guarded by Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) encryption to assure the privacy of your sensitive personal information."]},"id":"b33d4c06-95a7-4af5-b7f8-20a1a4294f60","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"886b419b-d2ae-4fe1-9a08-fed0a1144744","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["We appreciate the fact that Debt Consolidation Connection provides a reminder that debt consolidation is a serious step that you shouldn&#39;t take until you&#39;ve exhausted other potential debt remedies. Although the company is missing some features, we value the credit counseling help it provides for people when bad financial times come around."]},"id":"ddf5dd29-2a0b-4821-8e17-99ea6986f848","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_3294","url":"/debt-consolidation-connection-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"eli-mccormick","url":"/author/eli-mccormick","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Eli McCormick","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"CSoTtbWogSTgZ9Xgr3Anr9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2009-06-26T20:12:28Z"